						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Rāmaliṅgasvāmi temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1183, Durmati, Chaitra ba. 8, corresponding to 1261 A.D., March 25, Friday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to register the gift of land for a feeding house and a water pandal.</p>						

						</summary>
